videos.description: Terrapin forward Dodd gets up to block Ohio State's putback attempt
videos.headline: Maryland's Damonte Dodd rejects Trevor Thompson

videos.description: Terps forward Michal Cekovsky showing a strong inside presence with two slams vs. Ohio State
videos.headline: Michal Cekovsky throws down back-to-back dunks for Maryland.

videos.description: Maryland's Damonte Dodd skies for the rebound, then finishes with the slam.
videos.headline: Dodd slams home the putback dunk

videos.description: Buckeyes center Thompson gets the rebound and is fouled on the putback
videos.headline: Ohio State's Trevor Thompson grabs the offensive rebound and gets the layup

videos.description: Maryland's Gill gets the feed underneath the hoop for the bucket and the foul.
videos.headline: L.G. Gill gets the tough layup to fall

videos.description: Terps guard Huerter drains a deep three to give Maryland an 8-point lead late vs Ohio State.
videos.headline: Kevin Huerter sinks the long three to build Maryland lead
